# Lunity MCP

When using Lunity MCP tools (scene_load, entity_list, etc.), call **set_project** first with the project root:

```json
{"cwd": "/home/robin/workspaces/pong", "app": "pong"}
```

The `app` is optional (inferred from mix.exs if omitted). This is required because Lunity uses HTTP transport (stdio breaks due to group leader issues).
